(183, 1, '2012-10-25 18:50:17', '2012-10-25 18:50:17', '<div class="box">\r\n		<img src="http://3.brutelabs2.appspot.com/media/image/vision/vision.gif" style="width: 100%;">\r\n		<div id="vision_statement">\r\n			<span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> is out to prove that anyone can do good.  We use design and technology to create sustainable social entrepreneurship. Our small, all-volunteer team has launched 11 projects around the world and across a broad spectrum of causes; from <a href="cyclone.html">cyclone relief in Myanmar</a>, to <a target="_blank" href="http://welldone.org/">clean water wells in Ghana</a>, to a <a href="biodiesel.html">bio-diesel project with Stanford</a>. Our <a target="_blank" href="http://www.ssireview.org/opinion/entry/open_source_altruism/">open source altruism</a> has also garnered multiple design awards from <a target="_blank" href="http://causeaffect.aigasf.org/winners/community-development-2009">AIGA </a>and <a target="_blank" href="http://www.adobe.com/education/adaa/winners/2005/hm/projectopen.html">Adobe</a> as well as partnerships with local businesses, the city of San Jose, Google, Nike, Facebook and many more.<br><br><p></p>\r\n			<p><span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> was named to show the philosophy and attitude of the way we work:</p>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><strong>BRUTE</strong>: Do whatever it takes to get something done -- even if you have to roll up your sleeves and and get your hands a little dirty.</li>\r\n				<li><strong>LABS</strong>: We believe in constantly rapid prototyping and learning from our mistakes. We also want to be smart about what we do and be data driven.</li>\r\n			</ul><br>\r\n			<p><span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> achieves its mission through 9 essential principles:</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">1</span>\r\n			create and develop new ideas\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">2</span>\r\n			solve big problems\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We sweat the big stuff: poverty, hunger, homelessness, global health, education and countless others.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">3</span>\r\n			use good design to communicate powerfully \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			The right design amplifies the impact of a good message. We use simple, user-friendly, meaningful design.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">4</span>\r\n			act now\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">5</span>\r\n			inspire and mobilize others\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We want your help and we want you to get others to help. Rebuilding a city in the aftermath of a natural disaster or bringing clean water to those without it is work best done together. \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">6</span>\r\n			work differently\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re not afraid of shaking things up a bit. We''ll take the unconventional path over the conventional if it gets us there faster and has twice the impact.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">7</span>\r\n			deliver a measurable impact\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			Everything we do has to be measurable. 1,000 maps for the homeless. 7 clean water wells in Africa. 400 kids who are newly excited about being healthy. Accountability keeps us on track.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">8</span>\r\n			create open source solutions\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We strive to make every one of our projects something that anyone can do. Simple instructions, great design and plug-and-play solutions for social change.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">9</span>\r\n			do whatever it takes to get it done\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			This is the BRUTE in BRUTE LABS. We''ll be scrappy to get the job done, but will never compromise on delivering professional and polished results. \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '178-revision-4', '', '', '2012-10-25 18:50:17', '2012-10-25 18:50:17', '', 178, 'http://localhost:8888/2012/10/178-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(184, 1, '2012-10-25 18:59:07', '2012-10-25 18:59:07', '<div class="box">\r\n		<img src="http://3.brutelabs2.appspot.com/media/image/vision/vision.gif" style="width: 100%;">\r\n		<div id="vision_statement">\r\n			<span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> is out to prove that anyone can do good.  We use design and technology to create sustainable social entrepreneurship. Our small, all-volunteer team has launched 11 projects around the world and across a broad spectrum of causes; from <a href="cyclone.html">cyclone relief in Myanmar</a>, to <a target="_blank" href="http://welldone.org/">clean water wells in Ghana</a>, to a <a href="biodiesel.html">bio-diesel project with Stanford</a>. Our <a target="_blank" href="http://www.ssireview.org/opinion/entry/open_source_altruism/">open source altruism</a> has also garnered multiple design awards from <a target="_blank" href="http://causeaffect.aigasf.org/winners/community-development-2009">AIGA </a>and <a target="_blank" href="http://www.adobe.com/education/adaa/winners/2005/hm/projectopen.html">Adobe</a> as well as partnerships with local businesses, the city of San Jose, Google, Nike, Facebook and many more.<br><br><p></p>\r\n			<p><span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> was named to show the philosophy and attitude of the way we work:</p>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><strong>BRUTE</strong>: Do whatever it takes to get something done -- even if you have to roll up your sleeves and and get your hands a little dirty.</li>\r\n				<li><strong>LABS</strong>: We believe in constantly rapid prototyping and learning from our mistakes. We also want to be smart about what we do and be data driven.</li>\r\n			</ul><br>\r\n			<p><span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> achieves its mission through 9 essential principles:</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">1</span>create and develop new ideas\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">2</span>\r\n			solve big problems\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We sweat the big stuff: poverty, hunger, homelessness, global health, education and countless others.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">3</span>\r\n			use good design to communicate powerfully \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			The right design amplifies the impact of a good message. We use simple, user-friendly, meaningful design.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">4</span>\r\n			act now\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">5</span>\r\n			inspire and mobilize others\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We want your help and we want you to get others to help. Rebuilding a city in the aftermath of a natural disaster or bringing clean water to those without it is work best done together. \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">6</span>\r\n			work differently\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We''re not afraid of shaking things up a bit. We''ll take the unconventional path over the conventional if it gets us there faster and has twice the impact.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">7</span>\r\n			deliver a measurable impact\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			Everything we do has to be measurable. 1,000 maps for the homeless. 7 clean water wells in Africa. 400 kids who are newly excited about being healthy. Accountability keeps us on track.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">8</span>\r\n			create open source solutions\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			We strive to make every one of our projects something that anyone can do. Simple instructions, great design and plug-and-play solutions for social change.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="box principle">\r\n		<div class="title">\r\n			<span class="number">9</span>\r\n			do whatever it takes to get it done\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="content">\r\n			This is the BRUTE in BRUTE LABS. We''ll be scrappy to get the job done, but will never compromise on delivering professional and polished results. \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '178-revision-5', '', '', '2012-10-25 18:59:07', '2012-10-25 18:59:07', '', 178, 'http://localhost:8888/2012/10/178-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
