(185, 1, '2012-10-25 19:00:10', '2012-10-25 19:00:10', '<div class="box"><img style="width: 100%;" src="http://3.brutelabs2.appspot.com/media/image/vision/vision.gif" alt="" />\r\n<div id="vision_statement"><span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> is out to prove that anyone can do good. We use design and technology to create sustainable social entrepreneurship. Our small, all-volunteer team has launched 11 projects around the world and across a broad spectrum of causes; from <a href="cyclone.html">cyclone relief in Myanmar</a>, to <a href="http://welldone.org/" target="_blank">clean water wells in Ghana</a>, to a <a href="biodiesel.html">bio-diesel project with Stanford</a>. Our <a href="http://www.ssireview.org/opinion/entry/open_source_altruism/" target="_blank">open source altruism</a> has also garnered multiple design awards from <a href="http://causeaffect.aigasf.org/winners/community-development-2009" target="_blank">AIGA </a>and <a href="http://www.adobe.com/education/adaa/winners/2005/hm/projectopen.html" target="_blank">Adobe</a>as well as partnerships with local businesses, the city of San Jose, Google, Nike, Facebook and many more.<span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> was named to show the philosophy and attitude of the way we work:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>BRUTE</strong>: Do whatever it takes to get something done -- even if you have to roll up your sleeves and and get your hands a little dirty.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>LABS</strong>: We believe in constantly rapid prototyping and learning from our mistakes. We also want to be smart about what we do and be data driven.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="title">BRUTE LABS</span> achieves its mission through 9 essential principles:\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">1</span>create and develop new ideas</div>\r\n<div class="content">We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">2</span>solve big problems</div>\r\n<div class="content">We sweat the big stuff: poverty, hunger, homelessness, global health, education and countless others.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">3</span>use good design to communicate powerfully</div>\r\n<div class="content">The right design amplifies the impact of a good message. We use simple, user-friendly, meaningful design.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">4</span>act now</div>\r\n<div class="content">We''re out to change the world by pioneering new ideas and introducing new ways of thinking.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">5</span>inspire and mobilize others</div>\r\n<div class="content">We want your help and we want you to get others to help. Rebuilding a city in the aftermath of a natural disaster or bringing clean water to those without it is work best done together.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">6</span>work differently</div>\r\n<div class="content">We''re not afraid of shaking things up a bit. We''ll take the unconventional path over the conventional if it gets us there faster and has twice the impact.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">7</span>deliver a measurable impact</div>\r\n<div class="content">Everything we do has to be measurable. 1,000 maps for the homeless. 7 clean water wells in Africa. 400 kids who are newly excited about being healthy. Accountability keeps us on track.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">8</span>create open source solutions</div>\r\n<div class="content">We strive to make every one of our projects something that anyone can do. Simple instructions, great design and plug-and-play solutions for social change.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box principle">\r\n<div class="title"><span class="number">9</span>do whatever it takes to get it done</div>\r\n<div class="content">This is the BRUTE in BRUTE LABS. We''ll be scrappy to get the job done, but will never compromise on delivering professional and polished results.</div>\r\n</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '178-revision-6', '', '', '2012-10-25 19:00:10', '2012-10-25 19:00:10', '', 178, 'http://localhost:8888/2012/10/178-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
