(141, 7, 'bio', 'Every day in the news I learn about issues both here and abroad, and I can''t help but feel the urge to take action. BRUTE LABS allows me to team up with others to respond in creative and interesting ways. I''m excited to be part of a group that''s too impatient to do something about the issues we see. Born and raised in sunny California, I''ve been fortunate enough to get a college education and land a gig in corporate America. Outside the office, you can often spot me with my trusty camera, seeking adventure and going on spontaneous road trips.'),
