(173, 8, 'bio', 'I''m passionate about working with people seeking to affect change. There is no shortage of problems ailing the world in which we live. However, there is a shortage of people willing to get out and do the work needed to resolve these problems. I became frustrated while growing up in an environment filled with untapped potential and far too many dreams deferred. Today, my goal in life is to be an active player in the process of changing the world for the better; one person at a time.'),
