(350, 14, 'bio', 'Vanessa Maynard, born in 1986, is an Artist & Designer developing work in many design disciplines. She started studying design on her own since she was a child and dedicated her life to one of her biggest passions: creativity. In 2005, she was accepted to UCLA majoring in Design | Media Arts and graduating in Spring of 2009. Being moved by her own rebel personality, she was responsible for launching many projects in her hometown of Sacramento. As an artist, she has created many alter egos, where she expressed herself in very different ways. No Heart is her most known, with which Vanessa participated in many freelance projects in the music industry.'),
